data.description: This lovely 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath is an impressive home in the much-desired Wescott Plantation. The open floor plan has stainless steel appliances, laminated flooring downstairs and fenced backyard. Upstairs you will find 3 bedrooms, a loft and the laundry room. Don't miss this opportunity to own in Wescott at a great price.
